{"tid":131030,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"論毒撚無女原因","createTime":"2017-02-22T19:27:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T05:51:59.000Z","uid":48426,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e21878961dedf29a56421c18527b06da276fa3ef","tid":131030,"uid":48426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T19:27:40.000Z","msg":"不外乎性格 同 外觀既問題<br />\n<br />\n性格一時三刻改唔到就唔講啦<br />\n<br />\n外觀外面有樣野好緊要 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該</span></span><br />\n<br />\n注意下<span style=\"color: red;\">衛生</span>得唔得 <br />\n<br />\n發覺好多毒撚 頭都唔洗<br />\n<br />\n有小部分仲成浸味 好似幾日無沖涼咁<br />\n<br />\n就算我係男既都頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結論<br />\n唔該洗乾淨個頭先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b29ff87d095290522e30f1e751f966cc7cc4d6f","tid":131030,"uid":2022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T19:52:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e36fc55b370b25ac34bf67c7140db0e73f77adf","tid":131030,"uid":72638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T19:54:21.000Z","msg":"原因可以好多<br />\n<br />\n士但up幾個<br />\n<br />\n樣衰<br />\n冇錢<br />\n講野悶/唔啱話題"},{"pid":"cbe279a2cb88c182f9df8cb4018b5306199c6ac9","tid":131030,"uid":80580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T19:56:05.000Z","msg":"除左外表 全部都有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab6cc80700f8cbcfdf067a3547b379cf94504304","tid":131030,"uid":73202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T19:56:47.000Z","msg":"講野1999"},{"pid":"c9dca6c97d9a00ec4621a037ca101b4d730a53f4","tid":131030,"uid":86764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T19:56:59.000Z","msg":"點解可以唔沖涼，我真係忍唔到。樣衰就真係無得救"},{"pid":"07d222732a200de5db3093039bd5024aca2c3f65","tid":131030,"uid":48211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T19:57:43